Cross-Origin Resource Sharing</a> in the <i>Amazon Simple Storage Service Developer Guide</i>.</p> <p class=\"title\"> <b>Related Resources</b> </p> <ul> <li> <p> <a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/API/API_GetBucketCors.html\">GetBucketCors</a> </p> </li> <li> <p> <a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/API/API_DeleteBucketCors.html\">DeleteBucketCors</a> </p> </li> <li> <p> <a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/API/RESTOPTIONSobject.html\">RESTOPTIONSobject</a> </p> </li> </ul>",
