/AmazonS3/latest/API/API_GetBucketMetricsConfiguration.html\">GetBucketMetricsConfiguration</a> </p> </li> <li> <p> <a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/API/API_DeleteBucketMetricsConfiguration.html\">DeleteBucketMetricsConfiguration</a> </p> </li> </ul>",
        "responses": {
